	<Title>
		Is indulgence part of a healthy diet?
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;Sure, you know the importance of eating healthy foods. But is there room in a healthy diet for occasional splurges? You bet. Allow yourself an indulgence every now and then. If indulgence is the exception rather than the rule, you&apos;ll balance things out over the long term. What&apos;s important is that you eat healthy foods most of the time.&lt;/p&gt;
